WEBVTT

00:00:00.690 --> 00:00:03.666
It was the spring of 2011,

00:00:03.690 --> 00:00:06.492
and as they like to say
in commencement speeches,

00:00:06.516 --> 00:00:10.080
I was getting ready
to enter the real world.

00:00:10.727 --> 00:00:13.359
I had recently graduated from college

00:00:13.383 --> 00:00:16.123
and moved to Paris to start my first job.

00:00:16.990 --> 00:00:20.862
My dream was to become
a war correspondent,

00:00:20.886 --> 00:00:23.043
but the real world that I found

00:00:23.067 --> 00:00:27.347
took me into a really different
kind of conflict zone.

00:00:28.974 --> 00:00:30.998
At 22 years old,